            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/27668",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "bcmath is a php extension and not related to ZF.\nThis is not a issue of ZF.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-12-29T11:43:56.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-12-29T11:43:56.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/27676",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mdelanno",
                        "name": "mdelanno",
                        "displayName": "Maxence Delannoy",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "If you apply my patch of Zend_Locale_Math::normalize (see [http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/browse\/ZF-2878|ZF-2878]) and use it in Zend_Measure_Abstract::setType, the problem is resolved (unless you don't use bcmath, because I use bcmul and bcpow).\n\n{code}\n$value = call_user_func(Zend_Locale_Math::$mul, $value, Zend_Locale_Math::normalize($this->_units[$this->getType()][0]), 25);\n{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mdelanno",
                        "name": "mdelanno",
                        "displayName": "Maxence Delannoy",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-12-30T00:27:55.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-12-30T00:27:55.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/27747",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Issues of php itself of it's extensions can't be solved by ZF.\nTherefor this issue will be closed.",
